SIMPLE: importance
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Importance
<hw>Im*por"tance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>importance</ets>. See <er>Important</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The quality or state of being important; consequence; weight;
moment; significance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thy own <qex>importance</qex> know,⟦br⟧
Nor bound thy narrow views to things below.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Subject; matter.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Upon <qex>importance</qex> of so slight and trivial a nature.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Import; meaning; significance.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The wisest beholder could not say if the <qex>importance</qex>
were joy or sorrow.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>Importunity; solicitation.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>At our <qex>importance</qex> hither is he come.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Importancy</ent>⟦br⟧
